secubox-console (1.2.0-1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Standalone mode: Works without secubox-core installed
  * Fallback board detection for non-SecuBox systems
  * secubox-core moved from Depends to Recommends
  * Can now be installed on any Debian/Ubuntu system
  * Fix: BoardHeader import in SOC screens

