secubox-console (1.1.0-1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Add SOC integration for fleet monitoring
  * New screens: SOC Fleet, SOC Alerts, SOC Node Detail
  * SOC Gateway API client with HMAC authentication
  * Cross-node threat correlation display
  * Remote service management on edge nodes
  * Press 'f' for Fleet overview, 'a' for Alerts

 -- Gerald KERMA <devel@cybermind.fr>  Tue, 01 Apr 2026 14:00:00 +0200

secubox-console (1.0.0-1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Dashboard screen with live system metrics
  * Services screen with start/stop/restart/enable/disable
  * Network screen with interface classification
  * Logs screen with unit filtering and auto-scroll
  * Menu screen with system info and quick actions
  * Board-specific theming (MOCHAbin, ESPRESSObin, x64-vm, etc.)
  * Vim-style keyboard navigation (j/k/h/Enter)
  * Async API client for Unix socket communication
  * systemd service for TTY1 auto-start

 -- Gerald KERMA <devel@cybermind.fr>  Tue, 01 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0200
